* 外形尺寸: {{convert|5.5x4.0x3.3|km|mi|abbr=on}}<ref name=wild2>{{cite web |title=Comet 81P/Wild 2 |publisher=The Planetary Society |url=http://www.planetary.org/explore/topics/asteroids_and_comets/wild2.html |accessdate=December 16, 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090106004009/http://planetary.org./explore/topics/asteroids_and_comets/wild2.html |archivedate=2009年1月6日 |deadurl=no }}</ref>
* 密度: {{convert|0.6|g/cm3|lb/cuft|abbr=on}}<ref name=Britt2006>{{cite web
 |year        = 2006
 |title       = Small Body Density and Porosity: New Data, New Insights
