 |deadurl     = yes
}}</ref>
* 质量: {{convert|2.3|kg|lb|abbr=on}}{{e|13}}<ref>Using the [[體積#體積公式|volume of an ellipsoid]] of 5.5×4.0×3.3 km * a [[rubble_pile|rubble pile]] density of 0.6 g/cm³ yields a mass (m=d*v) of 2.28{{e|13}} kg</ref>

